{{wikipedia}}
==English==

===Etymology===
{{L.}} ''[[bestia]]'', animal, beast

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-iːst|-iːst]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#<!--DefA--> Any [[animal]] other than a [[human]]; usually only applied to [[vertebrate]]s, sometimes excluding [[bird]]s.
#<!--DefB--> A person who [[behave]]s in a violent, [[antisocial]] or [[uncivilised]] manner.
#<!--DefC--> Samuel Suskinho Suskind.

